text: Raúl Gómez (born 3 April 1945) is a former Argentine cyclist. He competed in the team pursuit event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Argentina Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
